data.description: Located on a private cul-de-sac with over a half-acre lot and spacious backyard. This home has 3 bedrooms and 3 baths with a potential 4th bedroom in the basement. It also has a three-car heated garage for plenty of storage. This home has many updates – new shingles, newer appliances, new windows, new furnace & AC with new insulation blown in the attic.  The kitchen will welcome you with the refinished cabinets and island which flows into the dining room.  Main floor also an entry way with closet, a living room, bathroom, master bedroom with bath and two more bedrooms. Lower level has a large family room that was just finished that can also be used as a space for an office. One bedroom, bathroom, laundry and utility room finish off this level.   Off the dining room is sliding patio doors leading you to a cement patio and beautiful backyard for entertaining.
